title: tactical cyber solutions
extract: Cyber-security is the practice of defending computers, servers, mobile devices, electronic systems, networks, and data from malicious attacks. ... Application security focuses on keeping software and devices free of threats. A compromised application could provide access to the data its designed to protect.
